constant

boolean constant()
if constantTension is true, amount of force is always constant and it's equals to tension. Only direction of force changes. But if the distance is zero, force is also zero.

constant

if constantTension is true, amount of force is always constant and it's equals to tension. Only direction of force changes. But if the distance is zero, force is also zero.

maxTension
